author: IGN
description:
2025 finally saw the long-awaited arrival of Nintendo’s next console: the Switch 2. But now, it’s time to turn the page to 2026 and talk about what’s in store for Switch 2’s sophomore year. With a new Mario movie and Pokemon's 30th anniversary on the way, 2026 will be a big year for Nintendo fans. Here’s what to expect from Nintendo in 2026.

#IGN #Nintendo #2026Games
title: What To Expect From Nintendo in 2026
